high_descs: Turn right then walk straight to the counter
Pick up the sponge on your right
Turn left then head to the right side of the stove
Put the sponge in pan
Pick up the pan with sponge
Turn right then stand on the left side of the sink counter
Put the pan with sponge on the right side of the sink counter
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with sponge on the right side of the sink counter

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter and turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the sponge off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the oven.
Put the sponge in the metal pan that is on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the sponge in it off of the stove.
Walk over to the section of counter to the left of the sink and turn to face the sink.
Put the metal pan with the sponge in it on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pan with a sponge in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the counter. Turn left to face the toaster.
Pick up the sponge from the right side of the counter.
Hold the sponge and take a few steps left, to go to the stove.
Place the sponge in the pan on the right front burner.
Pick up the pan from the right front burner.
Take the pan and take a few steps right to the corner of the counter. Turn so the the sink is on the left side.
Place the pan on the counter, past the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and sponge to the counter.
